  <text>
    <body>
      <p>
        <s>The <ref target="c12lk2_1" type="title">Sonnet 60</ref> is written by <ref target="c12lk2_1" type="author"><choice><orig>Shakespear</orig><reg>Shakespeare</reg></choice></ref>.</s>
        <s>Now you can read my paraphrase version.</s>
      </p>
      <lg type="sonnet">
        <lg type="1st quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>the waves <choice><orig>moves</orig><reg>move</reg></choice> the stones at</l>
            <l>the beach like minutes.</l>
          </s>
          <s>
            <l>The stones changing the place</l>
            <l>and they never go back on the place before, because of that, the stones fight to move forwards.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="2nd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>Birth is the start of life,</l>
            <l>from youth to being an adult,</l>
            <l>the fight against the darkness,</l>
            <l>the time we have is a gift.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="3rd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>The time goes by</l>
            <l>we don't keep the youth forever,</l>
            <l>we delve in the beauty of human and the rare truth.</l>
          </s>
          <s>
            <l>The death will come.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="final couplet">
          <s>
            <l>I hope you live your life because</l>
            <l>the death will come.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
